            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20of%20this%20scripture%20was%20demonstrated%20in%20Elijah's%20powerful%20confrontation%20with%20the%20prophets%20of%20Baal%20(1%20Kings%2018).%20First%2C%20God%20sent%20the%20drought%20to%20draw%20the%20people%20into%20the%20arena%20of%20decision.%20Then%2C%20He%20sent%20the%20fire%20to%20convince%20them%20of%20their%20sin.%20Finally%2C%20He%20sent%20the%20rain%20to%20remind%20them%20of%20His%20blessing.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20is%20able%20to%20do%20%22whatever%20pleases%20Him%2C%22%20at%20whatever%20time%20it%20pleases%20Him.%20When%20God%20was%20ready%20to%20visit%20the%20Gentiles%2C%20He%20did%20whatever%20pleased%20Him!%20But%20Peter%20had%20to%20spend%20time%20trying%20to%20convince%20the%20Jerusalem%20eldership%20that%20God%20was%20the%20Author%20of%20the%20Cornelius%20visitation%20(Acts%2011%3A4).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20is%20a%20mighty%20God%2C%20and%20His%20power%20can%20flow%20in%20whatever%20direction%20His%20love%20desires.%20Get%20out%20of%20the%20way%20and%20let%20God%20move!%20The%20result%20will%20be%20as%20it%20was%20in%20Acts%2011%3A21%20NIV%3A%20%22The%20Lord's%20hand%20was%20with%20them%2C%20and%20a%20great%20number%20of%20people%20turned%20and%20believed%20in%20the%20Lord.%22%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Kings.18:1-46",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%2018%3A1-46%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Contest%20on%20Mount%20Carmel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ELater%20on%2C%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20the%20drought%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Elijah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20present%20yourself%20to%20King%20Ahab.%20Tell%20him%20that%20I%20will%20soon%20send%20rain!%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Elijah%20went%20to%20appear%20before%20Ahab.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20famine%20had%20become%20very%20severe%20in%20Samaria.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Ahab%20summoned%20Obadiah%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20palace.%20(Obadiah%20was%20a%20devoted%20follower%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EOnce%20when%20Jezebel%20had%20tried%20to%20kill%20all%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20prophets%2C%20Obadiah%20had%20hidden%20100%26%23xA0%3Bof%20them%20in%20two%20caves.%20He%20put%20fifty%20prophets%20in%20each%20cave%20and%20supplied%20them%20with%20food%20and%20water.)%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAhab%20said%20to%20Obadiah%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20must%20check%20every%20spring%20and%20valley%20in%20the%20land%20to%20see%20if%20we%20can%20find%20enough%20grass%20to%20save%20at%20least%20some%20of%20my%20horses%20and%20mules.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20divided%20the%20land%20between%20them.%20Ahab%20went%20one%20way%20by%20himself%2C%20and%20Obadiah%20went%20another%20way%20by%20himself.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20Obadiah%20was%20walking%20along%2C%20he%20suddenly%20saw%20Elijah%20coming%20toward%20him.%20Obadiah%20recognized%20him%20at%20once%20and%20bowed%20low%20to%20the%20ground%20before%20him.%20%26%23x201C%3BIs%20it%20really%20you%2C%20my%20lord%20Elijah%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYes%2C%20it%20is%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Elijah%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20go%20and%20tell%20your%20master%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BElijah%20is%20here.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BOh%2C%20sir%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Obadiah%20protested%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwhat%20harm%20have%20I%20done%20to%20you%20that%20you%20are%20sending%20me%20to%20my%20death%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Ahab%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20I%20swear%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20that%20the%20king%20has%20searched%20every%20nation%20and%20kingdom%20on%20earth%20from%20end%20to%20end%20to%20find%20you.%20And%20each%20time%20he%20was%20told%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BElijah%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20here%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20King%20Ahab%20forced%20the%20king%20of%20that%20nation%20to%20swear%20to%20the%20truth%20of%20his%20claim.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20now%20you%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BGo%20and%20tell%20your%20master%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BElijah%20is%20here.%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20leave%20you%2C%20the%20Spirit%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20carry%20you%20away%20to%20who%20knows%20where.%20When%20Ahab%20comes%20and%20cannot%20find%20you%2C%20he%20will%20kill%20me.%20Yet%20I%20have%20been%20a%20true%20servant%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20all%20my%20life.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHas%20no%20one%20told%20you%2C%20my%20lord%2C%20about%20the%20time%20when%20Jezebel%20was%20trying%20to%20kill%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20prophets%3F%20I%20hid%20100%26%23xA0%3Bof%20them%20in%20two%20caves%20and%20supplied%20them%20with%20food%20and%20water.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20now%20you%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BGo%20and%20tell%20your%20master%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BElijah%20is%20here.%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2019%3B%20Sir%2C%20if%20I%20do%20that%2C%20Ahab%20will%20certainly%20kill%20me.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Elijah%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20swear%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Almighty%2C%20in%20whose%20presence%20I%20stand%2C%20that%20I%20will%20present%20myself%20to%20Ahab%20this%20very%20day.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Obadiah%20went%20to%20tell%20Ahab%20that%20Elijah%20had%20come%2C%20and%20Ahab%20went%20out%20to%20meet%20Elijah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Ahab%20saw%20him%2C%20he%20exclaimed%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BSo%2C%20is%20it%20really%20you%2C%20you%20troublemaker%20of%20Israel%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20made%20no%20trouble%20for%20Israel%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Elijah%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20and%20your%20family%20are%20the%20troublemakers%2C%20for%20you%20have%20refused%20to%20obey%20the%20commands%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20have%20worshiped%20the%20images%20of%20Baal%20instead.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20summon%20all%20Israel%20to%20join%20me%20at%20Mount%20Carmel%2C%20along%20with%20the%20450%26%23xA0%3Bprophets%20of%20Baal%20and%20the%20400%26%23xA0%3Bprophets%20of%20Asherah%20who%20are%20supported%20by%20Jezebel.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A19%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ewho%20eat%20at%20Jezebel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20table.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Ahab%20summoned%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20prophets%20to%20Mount%20Carmel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Elijah%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20them%20and%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHow%20much%20longer%20will%20you%20waver%2C%20hobbling%20between%20two%20opinions%3F%20If%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20God%2C%20follow%20him!%20But%20if%20Baal%20is%20God%2C%20then%20follow%20him!%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20the%20people%20were%20completely%20silent.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Elijah%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20the%20only%20prophet%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20is%20left%2C%20but%20Baal%20has%20450%26%23xA0%3Bprophets.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20bring%20two%20bulls.%20The%20prophets%20of%20Baal%20may%20choose%20whichever%20one%20they%20wish%20and%20cut%20it%20into%20pieces%20and%20lay%20it%20on%20the%20wood%20of%20their%20altar%2C%20but%20without%20setting%20fire%20to%20it.%20I%20will%20prepare%20the%20other%20bull%20and%20lay%20it%20on%20the%20wood%20on%20the%20altar%2C%20but%20not%20set%20fire%20to%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20call%20on%20the%20name%20of%20your%20god%2C%20and%20I%20will%20call%20on%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20The%20god%20who%20answers%20by%20setting%20fire%20to%20the%20wood%20is%20the%20true%20God!%26%23x201D%3B%20And%20all%20the%20people%20agreed.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_25%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Elijah%20said%20to%20the%20prophets%20of%20Baal%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20go%20first%2C%20for%20there%20are%20many%20of%20you.%20Choose%20one%20of%20the%20bulls%2C%20and%20prepare%20it%20and%20call%20on%20the%20name%20of%20your%20god.%20But%20do%20not%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20wood.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_18_26%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20prepared%20one%20of%20the%20bulls%20and%20placed%20it%20on%20the%20altar.%20Then%20they%20called%20on%20the%20name%20of%20Baal%20from%20morning%20until%20noontime%2C%20shouting%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3BBaal%2C%20answer%20us!%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20there%20was%20no%20reply%20of%20any%20kind.%20Then%20they%20danced%2C%20hobbling%20around%20the%20altar%20they%20had%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2F