2%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAs%20I%20began%20to%20speak%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Peter%20continued%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bthe%20Holy%20Spirit%20fell%20on%20them%2C%20just%20as%20he%20fell%20on%20us%20at%20the%20beginning.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_16%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20thought%20of%20the%20Lord%26%23x2019%3Bs%20words%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22red%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BJohn%20baptized%20with%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ein%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2011%3A16b.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20water%2C%20but%20you%20will%20be%20baptized%20with%20the%20Holy%20Spirit.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_17%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20since%20God%20gave%20these%20Gentiles%20the%20same%20gift%20he%20gave%20us%20when%20we%20believed%20in%20the%20Lord%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%20who%20was%20I%20to%20stand%20in%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20way%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_18%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20others%20heard%20this%2C%20they%20stopped%20objecting%20and%20began%20praising%20God.%20They%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20can%20see%20that%20God%20has%20also%20given%20the%20Gentiles%20the%20privilege%20of%20repenting%20of%20their%20sins%20and%20receiving%20eternal%20life.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_19%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Church%20in%20Ant