.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_24%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EBarnabas%20was%20a%20good%20man%2C%20full%20of%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20and%20strong%20in%20faith.%20And%20many%20people%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20Lord.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_25%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Barnabas%20went%20on%20to%20Tarsus%20to%20look%20for%20Saul.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_26%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20he%20found%20him%2C%20he%20brought%20him%20back%20to%20Antioch.%20Both%20of%20them%20stayed%20there%20with%20the%20church%20for%20a%20full%20year%2C%20teaching%20large%20crowds%20of%20people.%20(It%20was%20at%20Antioch%20that%20the%20believers%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A26%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Edisciples%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2011%3A29.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20were%20first%20called%20Christians.)%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_27%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20this%20time%20some%20prophets%20traveled%20from%20Jerusalem%20to%20Antioch.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_28%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20named%20Agabus%20stood%20up%20in%20one%20of%20the%20meetings%20and%20predicted%20by%20the%20Spirit%20that%20a%20great%20famine%20was%20coming%20upon%20the%20entire%20Roman%20world.%20(This%20was%20fulfilled%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20Claudius.)%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_29%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20believers%20in%20Antioch%20decided%20to%20send%20relief%20to%20the%20brothers%20and%20sisters%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A29%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20brothers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20Judea%2C%20everyone%20giving%20as%20much%20as%20they%20could.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22acts_11_30%22%20bk%3D%22acts%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20they%20did%2C%20entrusting%20their%20gifts%20to%20Barnabas%20and%20Saul%20to%20take%20to%20the%20elders%20of%20the%20church%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E"
